"09/26/2020 02:55am","178.166.8.244","0","+351918242756","francisca.a.campos@gmail.com","11-11-1990","En couple","Intendant Général - Régisseur - House manager"," 1720 CA","To whom it may concern,

We are a couple of Portuguese women with 27 and 29  searching for an exciting new challenge. So if you are looking for people with a very proactive and dynamic personality, we kindly ask you to take us into consideration.

Francisca with 29, it’s the head of the organization and detail, always looking to optimize any operation. Growing up by the sea and within a sailors’ family, she engaged in many different sports’ modalities and eventually took a Sports Management Degree. After building up 10 years of experience in the hospitality & leisure industry, including five-star hotels/resorts, she was recently part of the management team of DoubleTree Westminster by Hilton, performing the role of Duty Manager, supervising (among othes) the Housekeeping, F&B, Maintenance and Security departments.

Catarina with 27, it’s the head of creativity and innovation, always looking to be one step ahead of everything. With an avant-garde mind and growing up in the countryside, at a very young age she found a way to express herself through performing arts but, eventually fell in love for bartending and mixology, which found out to have a natural talent and quickly progressed in her career, becoming the Deputy Head Bartender in one of the most well-known fine-dining’s restaurants in the city of Lisbon.

We have been together for more than 4 years and we absolutely love living and hosting together. We enjoy everything that involves sharing a home, due our shared interests, habits and values, for example the love for cooking and haute cuisine. Both of us connect well with people and have a good empathy with the groups that we work with, full of great sense of humor and outgoing and caring personalities. So much that in the past, Francisca hosted and presented an extreme sports segment on Portuguese television, on a weekly basis and Catarina is constantly required to act or model for campaigns for the music industry, advertising, etc.

We thank you in advance for your attention and look forward for your feedback! 

